verbose_text: When information on use of diuretics, the use of ACE inhibitors / ARBs, or the type of diabetes was added to the multivariable regression analyses, only the type of diabetes was a significant covariate for the association between urinary KIM-1, NAG, NGAL, cystatin C, and H-FABP with albuminuria.
evidence: association between urinary KIM-1, NAG, NGAL, cystatin C, and H-FABP
